Backlog is a project management, hosting service.
http://backlog.com, http://www.backlog.jp (Japanese)

Install Notes
-------------

1. **base_url** is a API URL. e.g. if the Space ID is example, then the api_url will be https://example.backlog.com https://example.backlog.jp or https://example.backlogtool.com

2. **api_key** and **password** - api_key of a Backlog user that can post comment and update issue.

You can specify issue keys (e.g. DORA-1) and status keywords (#fixed, #closed) to change issue status (Resolved, Closed).
